file.tree.analyzer

Class FileInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • file.tree.analyzer.FileInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FileInfo>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DiffInfo

    public class FileInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<FileInfo>
    Entity class for storing information about file or directory. In case of directory, all children are accessible using instance of this class.

      • FileInfo

        public FileInfo(java.nio.file.Path file)
        Constructor for cases when we only know path to the file. Tries to set name, path, and directory attributes, accesibility is set to false (this means that the file/folder is not readable).
        Parameters:
